thread.title_full: Kitchen Cabinet Kings reviewed by Kristen Tomczak

author: Kristen Tomczak
title: Kristen Tomczak
text: I am pleased with my purchase from Kitchen Cabinet Kings. Ordering was simple, and delivery was very fast. There was one cabinet that came damaged on the door, but customer service was great and they replaced the door at no cost. Great quality with the soft close, and hard wood boxes. Overall, a very satisfied customer!
